title: Nato's Assistant Secretary General to visit Finland (Government of Finland)
text: ( Source : Government of Finland ) Nato 's Assistant Secretary General Patrick Auroy will visit Finland on 14 to 16 October 2015 . His host will be Director General Jukka Juusti, Head of the Resource Policy Department in the Ministry of Defence .
